LeBron James CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
CLEVELAND -- LeBron James unveiled an interesting new hairstyle on Instagram over the weekend. 
Instagram users were treated to the new 'do, which was clearly a wig, part of an alter ego James deemed "JP" for James "Plaid" Jackson, according to the caption. 
James posted several photos from a birthday party, which was also attended by other Cleveland personalities, like DJ Steph Floss.
